♪A black chess piece♪

00:00:19.660 --> 00:00:23.140
♪Whose game did he stumble into?♪

00:00:23.740 --> 00:00:27.620
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

00:00:29.420 --> 00:00:33.340
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:40.020
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:42.620
♪I will remember♪

00:00:42.780 --> 00:00:46.660
♪Those days long past♪

00:00:47.660 --> 00:00:51.580
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

00:00:52.220 --> 00:00:53.660
♪Ten thousand years ago♪

00:00:53.780 --> 00:00:57.500
♪Did you once walk this shore?♪

00:00:57.740 --> 00:01:02.940
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:05.100
♪I am lost yet willing♪

00:01:05.180 --> 00:01:09.580
♪Still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:17.100
♪Until all things fade away♪

00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:27.220
♪The stars will remember us♪

00:01:27.220 --> 00:01:28.220
[Love & Crown]

00:01:28.220 --> 00:01:29.980
[Adapted from the novel "My Queen" by Xie Lounan]

00:01:29.980 --> 00:01:32.980
[Episode 11]

00:01:36.310 --> 00:01:38.770
The best effect of birth-control tea

00:01:39.150 --> 00:01:40.130
lasts only three days.

00:01:44.350 --> 00:01:47.570
So this is what you call keeping me safe?

00:01:51.560 --> 00:01:52.260
Yes.

00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:08.100
Well.

00:02:10.820 --> 00:02:14.590
♪Snow veils the mountains, love endures beyond life and death...♪

00:02:14.590 --> 00:02:16.060
Then it must be to go along

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.290
with His Majesty's wishes.

00:02:21.940 --> 00:02:26.500
♪All his life, there's no escape♪

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:32.780
♪Faint fireflies fade into late autumn♪

00:02:33.940 --> 00:02:37.980
♪I am foolish, I believe, and I am still waiting for you♪

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:45.140
♪Where has the message in the bottle drifted to?♪

00:02:45.260 --> 00:02:50.220
♪Who is reading this heart?♪

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:56.180
♪In ten thousand years, what will still remain?♪

00:02:56.420 --> 00:03:01.540
♪Will anyone still love with an unchanging heart?♪

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:07.700
♪I will remember those days long past♪

00:03:09.420 --> 00:03:13.340
♪As the wind drifts with the white sail♪

00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:19.020
♪Ten thousand years ago, did you once walk this shore?♪

00:03:19.620 --> 00:03:24.740
♪Why can't our bond be severed in this life?♪

00:03:25.340 --> 00:03:31.780
♪I am lost yet willing, still I love you with a steadfast heart♪

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:39.580
♪Until all things fade away...♪

00:03:39.590 --> 00:03:40.570
Why?

00:03:43.910 --> 00:03:45.290
If you truly wish to ask me,

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:47.730
then I shall tell you.

00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:52.060
I cannot have

00:03:52.800 --> 00:03:54.450
a child of the Ling bloodline.

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:01.170
Liar.

00:04:02.100 --> 00:04:03.940
♪The silent tide♪

00:04:04.060 --> 00:04:06.060
♪Carries away every answer♪

00:04:06.420 --> 00:04:08.660
♪The chessboard is etched with rust...♪

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:11.130
Liar!

00:04:12.180 --> 00:04:13.700
♪Never once gave up...♪

00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:17.730
Which words of yours are true, and which are false?

00:04:19.740 --> 00:04:24.860
♪A fate of ten thousand years all our love and wrongs...♪

00:04:27.870 --> 00:04:29.810
You push me away ten paces,

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:31.730
then pull me back again.

00:04:33.800 --> 00:04:35.250
Do you truly find this amusing?

00:04:43.540 --> 00:04:49.620
♪The stars will remember us♪

00:05:09.500 --> 00:05:13.300
[Wuying Hall]

00:05:26.950 --> 00:05:27.700
Your Majesty.

00:05:29.750 --> 00:05:30.810
You may return.

00:05:31.360 --> 00:05:33.810
There is no need to administer the needles today.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:39.930
Why does Your Majesty not tell Her Majesty the truth?

00:05:40.830 --> 00:05:42.050
Why not tell her

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:43.980
what manner of cruel man her father is?

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:49.370
Ling Xuefeng has always showered her with affection.

00:05:49.950 --> 00:05:52.340
How could she possibly accept such a truth?

00:05:52.510 --> 00:05:53.580
Must all of this

00:05:54.190 --> 00:05:55.900
fall upon Your Majesty alone?

00:05:58.360 --> 00:05:59.370
I am used to it.

00:06:01.480 --> 00:06:03.850
Your Majesty has grown used to Her Majesty's many misunderstandings.

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:05.700
So used, even,

00:06:06.270 --> 00:06:07.900
that you would give up the life-saving cure.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.020
Is this the sincerity Your Majesty speaks of?

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:14.020
Regarding the Frost Reed,

00:06:14.310 --> 00:06:16.700
I hope the Imperial Preceptor will never mention it again,

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.340
especially before the Empress.

00:06:19.510 --> 00:06:20.780
If I discover

00:06:21.190 --> 00:06:22.490
that you defy my will,

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:25.290
do not blame me for showing no mercy.

00:06:35.870 --> 00:06:36.540
Yes,

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:37.930
Your Majesty.

00:07:05.190 --> 00:07:05.780
Your Majesty.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.810
Song Lanxi, the lady-in-waiting, seeks an audience.

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:09.810
Miss Ling.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:11.900
It is me.

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:22.900
Zhong Lin.

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:24.700
What...

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:25.850
What has happened?

00:07:26.390 --> 00:07:27.980
It truly is you.

00:07:46.950 --> 00:07:49.050
So much has happened in so little time.

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:50.850
I told you that Bai Chifan

00:07:50.870 --> 00:07:52.140
was never anything good.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:55.490
Cangcang.

00:07:56.070 --> 00:07:57.700
Why don't we return to Southern Chu?

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:58.780
We can restore Fenglai Pavilion.

00:08:00.070 --> 00:08:01.370
Restore Fenglai Pavilion...

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:07.370
Can I still become the Ling Cangcang I once was?

00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:08.490
Of course you can.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:09.460
Why wouldn't you?

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:11.930
You are the famed heroine everyone speaks of.

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:22.700
Xiao Qianqing...

00:08:23.310 --> 00:08:24.540
Would he even let you go?

00:08:25.310 --> 00:08:26.410
Why should I care?

00:08:26.950 --> 00:08:28.290
He certainly can't stop me.

00:08:30.950 --> 00:08:32.010
I cannot leave yet.

00:08:33.870 --> 00:08:35.010
There is something I must do.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.770
What is it?

00:08:41.360 --> 00:08:43.960
You said His Majesty gave Her Majesty birth-control tea?

00:08:44.390 --> 00:08:44.980
Yes.

00:08:45.270 --> 00:08:46.300
Rumors are already spreading in the palace.

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:46.770
They say...

00:08:46.790 --> 00:08:47.770
They say what?

00:08:47.910 --> 00:08:48.700
They say His Majesty

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.700
does not want the Empress to bear a child of the Ling bloodline.

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:53.360
Xiao Huan is out of his mind!

00:08:53.550 --> 00:08:54.340
Father.

00:08:54.510 --> 00:08:55.370
If this continues,

00:08:55.670 --> 00:08:57.060
Cangcang will be doomed sooner or later.

00:08:58.840 --> 00:08:59.730
She will not.

00:09:01.270 --> 00:09:02.940
A man at death's door

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:04.730
is hardly worth fearing.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:06.700
Xianxue.

00:09:07.270 --> 00:09:08.980
Contact Cangcang at once.

00:09:10.150 --> 00:09:11.980
She must be heartbroken right now.

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:15.220
This is our best chance

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:17.060
to obtain the Moon-Eclipse.

00:09:17.510 --> 00:09:18.420
Yes, Father.

00:09:18.420 --> 00:09:19.790
[Brush and Ink]

00:09:19.790 --> 00:09:20.490
Wait.

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:30.250
Xianxue.

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.580
I know you worry for Cangcang.

00:09:35.790 --> 00:09:37.420
As her father, so do I.

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:41.820
If you wish to truly protect her,

00:09:42.390 --> 00:09:43.980
then you must first

00:09:45.150 --> 00:09:46.460
become stronger.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:07.460
Master.

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:11.770
No...

00:10:18.150 --> 00:10:18.730
Your Majesty.

00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:19.730
What troubles you?

00:10:19.840 --> 00:10:20.890
Another nightmare?

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:23.420
It is nothing.

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:25.980
Your Majesty's health has only just improved.

00:10:26.000 --> 00:10:27.340
You are still vulnerable to outside chills.

00:10:28.510 --> 00:10:30.490
You have stayed inside the chambers for days.

00:10:30.910 --> 00:10:32.890
You should at least go out and take in some sunlight.

00:10:34.390 --> 00:10:34.940
Well.

00:10:57.140 --> 00:10:59.080
[Wuying Hall]

00:10:59.080 --> 00:10:59.700
Your Majesty.

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:01.490
I have already done as ordered

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:03.100
and deliberately leaked the news to Grand Tutor Ling.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.700
May he restrain himself,

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:09.700
and cease using Cangcang again.

00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:11.250
But I have just learned

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:12.460
that Her Majesty has left the palace

00:11:12.750 --> 00:11:14.340
and headed toward the hot-spring palace residence.

00:11:21.720 --> 00:11:23.420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:11:23.550 --> 00:11:26.220
We greet Your Majesty.

00:11:36.540 --> 00:11:43.140
[Lingquan Palace]

00:12:12.720 --> 00:12:14.700
Your Majesty is not in a rush to depart, right?

00:12:15.390 --> 00:12:16.460
If not,

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:20.100
I would like to accompany Your Majesty in a game of chess.

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:21.370
Would that be agreeable?

00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:22.700
My chess skills

00:12:22.720 --> 00:12:24.180
were all taught by the Grand Tutor.

00:12:24.550 --> 00:12:27.010
Today, Grand Tutor may judge for yourself

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:29.420
whether I have improved.

00:12:37.130 --> 00:12:38.240
In recent days,

00:12:38.350 --> 00:12:40.990
I heard a curious tale.

00:12:42.150 --> 00:12:44.340
It is said that the magistrate of Mixian

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.340
tried a peculiar case.

00:12:45.440 --> 00:12:46.770
Two women,

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:48.300
both claiming a single infant.

00:12:48.320 --> 00:12:51.250
Each insisting the child was her own.

00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:52.530
Your Majesty.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:55.700
If this case were left to you,

00:12:56.550 --> 00:12:58.130
how would you judge it?

00:12:58.240 --> 00:12:59.420
Let the two women

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:01.490
each take one of the child's hands.

00:13:01.720 --> 00:13:02.980
The infant is frail

00:13:03.240 --> 00:13:04.460
and cannot endure such struggle.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:06.130
To keep the child unharmed,

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:07.700
the one who lets go first

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:09.940
must be the true mother.

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:14.770
Your Majesty is indeed wise.

00:13:15.320 --> 00:13:18.980
Victory and defeat lie between a single thought.

00:13:21.070 --> 00:13:22.650
Because she could not bear it,

00:13:22.650 --> 00:13:24.100
she chose to let go.

00:13:25.140 --> 00:13:27.180
But whether that is victory or defeat,

00:13:28.250 --> 00:13:29.410
in truth,

00:13:29.720 --> 00:13:31.380
it is difficult to say.

00:13:37.030 --> 00:13:38.460
Your Majesty grew careless.

00:13:46.510 --> 00:13:47.770
Your teachings,

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:49.060
I have taken to heart.

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:51.700
I also remember

00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:53.180
Grand Tutor once taught me...

00:13:53.510 --> 00:13:54.580
Pride must not rise,

00:13:54.600 --> 00:13:55.700
the heart must not overflow.

00:13:56.870 --> 00:13:58.220
As for where the blossoms fall,

00:13:58.270 --> 00:13:59.370
nothing is certain yet.

00:14:16.000 --> 00:14:17.370
Your Majesty is indeed

00:14:17.390 --> 00:14:20.010
the finest student I have ever taught.

00:14:20.270 --> 00:14:22.180
This strike, sharp and decisive,

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:23.060
is fine play.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.730
It is Grand Tutor's teachings that were fine.

00:14:27.390 --> 00:14:28.940
But Grand Tutor need not worry.

00:14:29.750 --> 00:14:31.100
In me,

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:33.100
there will never be a woman's softness.

00:14:45.630 --> 00:14:46.590
- Hongqing. - Yes.

00:14:47.030 --> 00:14:47.940
Grand Tutor is weary.

00:14:48.200 --> 00:14:50.340
Escort him to the side hall to rest for the night.

00:14:50.960 --> 00:14:51.530
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:37.460
Have you decided?

00:15:38.030 --> 00:15:39.530
Will you truly retrieve the Moon-Eclipse?

00:15:44.320 --> 00:15:45.180
You are right.

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:46.980
Only if the Moon-Eclipse is in my hands

00:15:47.000 --> 00:15:48.130
will it be safest.

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:51.300
I must destroy it myself.

00:15:51.720 --> 00:15:53.770
Only then can I ensure it never harms the world again.

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:08.370
Master...

00:16:09.150 --> 00:16:10.850
You wished for this as well,

00:16:11.240 --> 00:16:11.940
did you not?

00:17:21.590 --> 00:17:22.180
Cangcang!

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:26.380
Cangcang, are you all right?

00:17:28.960 --> 00:17:29.900
We must leave first.

00:17:29.920 --> 00:17:31.290
We will destroy the Moon-Eclipse later.

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:33.940
Go.

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:57.940
Your Majesty.

00:17:58.830 --> 00:18:00.330
The assassin who threatened the Empress has been seized.

00:18:01.030 --> 00:18:02.530
This was found on his person.

00:18:09.830 --> 00:18:11.140
He did not threaten me.

00:18:11.400 --> 00:18:12.460
I summoned him.

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:14.220
Are you certain

00:18:14.510 --> 00:18:16.460
you have not been deceived by this thief?

00:18:16.960 --> 00:18:18.140
The one who deceived me...

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:20.940
Was it not you?

00:18:25.510 --> 00:18:27.700
Your Majesty speaks the sweetest words,

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:30.810
yet does the things that hurt me most.

00:18:33.720 --> 00:18:34.700
I was a fool.

00:18:36.480 --> 00:18:38.250
Time and again I let you deceive me,

00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:40.980
and still believed you.

00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:51.250
Cangcang.

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:52.860
I warned you long ago.

00:18:53.310 --> 00:18:54.250
You should never trust him.

00:18:55.110 --> 00:18:56.140
Take him away.

00:18:56.400 --> 00:18:57.180
Yes.

00:19:00.270 --> 00:19:01.770
I told you the fault is not his.

00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:03.570
This matter has nothing to do with him.

00:19:03.920 --> 00:19:04.810
The fault lies with me.

00:19:35.200 --> 00:19:36.250
The one who deceived me...

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:37.810
Was it not you?

00:19:39.000 --> 00:19:41.010
Your Majesty speaks the sweetest words,

00:19:41.510 --> 00:19:43.050
yet does the things that wound me.

00:19:44.550 --> 00:19:45.700
I was a fool.

00:19:47.270 --> 00:19:48.940
Time and again I let you deceive me,

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:51.700
and still believed you.

00:20:38.030 --> 00:20:39.460
What brings you here?

00:20:45.790 --> 00:20:46.700
I heard

00:20:47.510 --> 00:20:49.460
one must not drink while soaking in the hot spring.

00:20:52.070 --> 00:20:53.290
If you have something to say,

00:20:54.270 --> 00:20:55.380
you may speak plainly.

00:21:18.720 --> 00:21:20.050
If one drinks this wine,

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:26.420
it will make one

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:31.460
lose all sense and restraint

00:21:33.110 --> 00:21:34.530
and lose all control.

00:21:41.590 --> 00:21:43.090
For Luo Xianxue,

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:45.530
you dare tease me?

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:51.700
It is from the heart.

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:05.250
Very well.

00:22:20.720 --> 00:22:21.530
Just now,

00:22:21.960 --> 00:22:23.730
did you not say it was from the heart?

00:22:27.830 --> 00:22:28.730
Let him go.

00:22:30.790 --> 00:22:31.730
Let him go?

00:22:33.160 --> 00:22:35.180
I wish nothing more than to have him torn apart.

00:22:35.790 --> 00:22:37.330
Yet you ask me to spare him?

00:22:47.030 --> 00:22:48.460
Then let me hate you.

00:23:04.160 --> 00:23:05.700
For Luo Xianxue,

00:23:06.110 --> 00:23:08.220
you truly dare to do anything.

00:23:09.480 --> 00:23:10.570
I will not kill you.

00:23:11.550 --> 00:23:12.330
After all,

00:23:13.160 --> 00:23:14.730
I cannot let the Ling clan

00:23:15.070 --> 00:23:16.250
follow me to the grave.

00:23:46.980 --> 00:23:51.020
[Emperor's Seal]

00:23:56.830 --> 00:23:58.250
Peace to Your Majesty.

00:24:00.440 --> 00:24:00.940
Open the door.

00:24:01.030 --> 00:24:01.700
Yes.

00:24:09.590 --> 00:24:10.380
Luo.

00:24:11.680 --> 00:24:12.330
Cangcang.

00:24:13.110 --> 00:24:13.900
Release him.

00:24:14.310 --> 00:24:15.420
Without His Majesty's order,

00:24:15.510 --> 00:24:16.290
I dare not.

00:24:18.790 --> 00:24:20.010
This is His Majesty's order.

00:24:21.720 --> 00:24:22.220
Yes.

00:24:40.480 --> 00:24:41.090
Cangcang.

00:24:42.160 --> 00:24:43.290
Luo, go now.

00:24:43.310 --> 00:24:44.180
Do not return.

00:24:44.200 --> 00:24:44.900
You are not leaving?

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:45.980
Let us leave together.

00:24:47.070 --> 00:24:47.810
I cannot leave.

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:48.770
Nor can I go.

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:50.770
But you are releasing a major criminal.

00:24:50.790 --> 00:24:52.090
He will not spare you easily.

00:24:52.200 --> 00:24:54.010
I promised to keep you safe,

00:24:54.110 --> 00:24:55.010
so I must do so.

00:24:55.960 --> 00:24:56.730
As for me,

00:24:57.350 --> 00:24:58.140
you need not worry.

00:24:58.270 --> 00:24:59.180
I have my own way.

00:25:00.030 --> 00:25:01.050
There is no time. Go.

00:25:11.580 --> 00:25:15.860
[Lingquan Palace]

00:25:22.720 --> 00:25:23.770
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:27.010
Good.

00:25:27.830 --> 00:25:28.700
Very good.

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:31.180
I defied Your Majesty's decree.

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:32.250
I ask for punishment.

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:33.330
My empress,

00:25:33.590 --> 00:25:35.290
you have nothing to explain?

00:25:35.720 --> 00:25:36.220
Nothing.

00:25:39.880 --> 00:25:41.420
The Empress has failed in virtue.

00:25:41.720 --> 00:25:43.010
Return to the palace and remain confined for three days.

00:25:43.200 --> 00:25:45.700
Kneel and copy the scriptures in repentance.

00:25:45.750 --> 00:25:46.530
I accept the decree.

00:25:46.720 --> 00:25:47.700
And give thanks for the grace.

00:25:57.440 --> 00:25:58.290
Do you think

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:00.570
I will spare Luo Xianxue?

00:26:01.060 --> 00:26:02.940
♪Sky so vast♪

00:26:03.620 --> 00:26:07.060
♪The fading dusk sinks into the river♪

00:26:09.980 --> 00:26:11.740
♪The wild geese cry long♪

00:26:12.540 --> 00:26:15.980
♪Tonight my homeland feels as distant as a foreign shore♪

00:26:18.700 --> 00:26:20.620
♪Snow so white♪

00:26:21.460 --> 00:26:24.860
♪Bare branches haunt the empty lanes♪

00:26:25.180 --> 00:26:28.780
♪Half the city in rain half in ruin♪

00:26:29.620 --> 00:26:33.820
♪Only the dying sun sinks to the western frontier♪

00:26:36.180 --> 00:26:38.260
♪The azure battle flag♪

00:26:38.460 --> 00:26:40.580
♪Burning through the war flames for you♪

00:26:40.620 --> 00:26:42.780
♪Honouring the fallen of our land♪

00:26:44.980 --> 00:26:46.780
♪Looking back across the ends of the earth♪

00:26:47.260 --> 00:26:51.980
♪Countless loyal spirits drift with no place to return♪

00:26:53.940 --> 00:26:56.180
♪The ancient chronicles stand vast and cold♪

00:26:56.380 --> 00:26:58.460
♪Etching only a half lost chapter♪

00:26:58.500 --> 00:26:59.860
♪Buried beneath the drifting sand♪

00:26:59.940 --> 00:27:02.140
♪Each word strikes with solemn weight♪

00:27:02.900 --> 00:27:04.540
♪Let love and hate both fade away♪

