♪The dragon patterned sword breaks♪

00:27:06.700 --> 00:27:09.740
♪Still faintly warm with blood♪

00:27:15.780 --> 00:27:19.140
♪A few strokes of history's ink♪

00:27:24.780 --> 00:27:28.820
♪Bury the boy I once was♪

